Variable.name: LOGLEVEL
Variable.Description: Stores the level of details the Analytics server should log the activities it is performing in the log file (NQquery.log). Even though this session is part of the session variables, out of the box it is hard coded in the Initialization block (Login Properties), so it's value is the same for the whole server instance. This can be changed though, if the Administrator wants to provide a table with different login levels for different users.
